What you need to know:  World champion Conseslus Kipruto will lead the Kenyan team of Commonwealth Games silver medallist Abraham Kibiwott, Olympics silver medalist Benjamin Kigen and the World Under-20 champion Amos SeremKipruto, who is seeking to wrestle the title back from Morocco’s Soufiane El Bakkali, ran his first race in a year at last week’s Athletics Kenya National track and field championships at KasaraniKipruto is looking forward to retaining his world title at the 2022 World Athletics Championships slated for July 15 to 24 in Eugene, USA